high_descs: Move to the long black table on the left wall, turn left to face the watches on the table.
Pick up the rear watch on the table.
Bring the watch around to the other side of the table and face that same wall, towards the tissue box.
Put the watch on the plate on the table.
Pick up the plate with watch on the table.
Head right, around the couch, to the coffee table on the other side of the couch.
Put the plate with watch on it, on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with watch on the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn to your left and move forward into the aisle way between the table and the wall, then turn to your right and walk to the end table on your left.
Pick up the watch on the front, right corner of the end table, in front of the other watch.
Turn to your right and go past the table, then turn to your right again and walk between the table and the back of the couch, to the second chair on your right.
Place the watch on the plate, in front of the chair, on the table.
Pick up the plate, with the watch on it.
Turn to your right and walk to the end of the couch, turn to your right again to get to the front of the couch, then turn right and go to the coffee table in front of you.
Place the plate with the watch on it, on the back, right corner of the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate containing a watch on the coffee table.

high_descs: Move forward and face the black desk to your left.
Take the watch off of the black desk in front of you.
Turn right, go around the table and face the table to your right.
Place the watch on top of the plate on the table in front of you.
Take the plate with the watch on the table in front of you.
Turn right, go around the couch and face the center table to your right.
Place the plate with the watch on the table in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place the watch on the center table.
